## Error Boundaries

- **Global error boundary** catches unhandled errors, shows 500 page
- **Feature-level boundaries** catch errors in specific sections without killing the whole app
- **Never show raw errors** to users - log them, show safe user-facing text
- **Retry mechanism** for transient failures (network errors)

---

## Images & Media

- **Lazy load** images below the fold
- **Responsive images** with srcset or equivalent
- **Placeholder** while loading (blur hash, solid color, or skeleton)
- **Max file size** indication on upload forms
- **Fallback** for broken images (default placeholder graphic)
